items.headline: LEARN HOW TO OPEN THE DOOR TO INNER SILENCE, MENTAL CLARITY AND MINDFULNESS
objectives_summary: After this course you will know how much your life depends on what you think and what thoughts you give your beliefs. In addition, you will be able to direct your life from the inside out - through the power of your thoughts - into the pathways in which you really want to direct it. With the knowledge you gain from practicing this course, you can see old and unnecessary habits more clearly, look at them neutrally, and integrate new, more helpful ones into your life. With the inner knowingness of intentionally allowing the silence of thought to create infinite inner space, you will be able to free your life from anything obstructive while creating the best version of yourself.
